Political activist Lauretta Onochie has reacted after the saga circulating on social media that the All Progressives Congress (APC) presidential candidate did not attend primary and secondary school and that he has no university certificate. Lauretta Onochie stated that it is the handwork of the opposition who are trying to discredit Asiwaju Bola Tinubu.
Onochie revealed that everyone should know that a man like Asiwaju Bola Tinubu not have attended primary and secondary school. She revealed that he used that opportunity to gain more popularity because the news has circulated in Nigeria, making him gain more popularity as he edges close to his presidential ambit
The popular socialist noted that the opposition Asiwaju Bola Tinubu are doing themselves more harm than good by trying to spread such need about Tinubu because he’s being made to gain popularity among those who don’t know him.
She said even those living in rural areas who have no access to internet gadgets have heard about the saga surrounding Tinubu’s certificate.
Reports even revealed that Asiwaju earlier revealed that he did not attend primary and secondary school, noting that his certificate was stolen by military men.


